txt-to-video-extractor/
│
├── README.md            # Project overview and instructions
├── requirements.txt     # Dependencies (if using Python)
├── extractor.py         # Main code for extracting video from TXT
├── utils.py             # Utility functions for processing text or video
├── assets/              # Folder for assets (e.g., sample images, fonts)
│   ├── font.ttf         # Example font for text rendering
│   └── example_video.mp4 # Example video file for testing
├── tests/               # Unit tests
│   ├── test_extractor.py
│   └── test_utils.py
└── .gitignore           # Ignore unnecessary files (e.g., Python bytecode)
